quran[12]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,88,"Ngasinyyikolondochesya ata panandi meso genu yatujisengwachisye nayo mikutula jakulekanganalekangana ja ŵanganyao (achimakafilio), soni ngasimwadandaulila. Ni mwatuluchisyeje lipapiko lyenu ŵakulupilila (pakwatendela chanasa)."
  15,89,"Soni jilani: “Chisimu une ni nkutetela jwakuonechela (ngangusisa chilichose kogopela kuti itakwisa muimpatile ilagasyo).”"
  15,90,"Mpela yatwatite pakutulusya (ilagasyo) kwa akugaŵanya."
  16,67,"Ni mu isogosi yatende ni zabibu nkasalinganyaga kuumila mwalakwemo yakumwa yakolelwasya kwisa soni lisiki lyambone. Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo (chakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) kwa ŵandu ŵaakwete lunda."
  16,68,"Soni Ambuje ŵenu ŵasijuwulile nyuchi kuti: “Lilinganyichisyani majumba m’matumbi kwisa soni mu itela ni (m’misinga) jaakukolekaga (ŵandu).”"
  16,69,"“Kaneko nillyeje isogosi yantundu uliose, basi ni n’jendeje m’matala ga Ambuje ŵenu gagajepepasyidwe (kukwenu).” Ikasakopokaga mu ndumbo syakwe yakumwa yakulekangana ntundu wakwe (wauli uchi), mwalakwemo mwana ntela waŵandu (wakupolela ilwele yaijinji). Chisimu mu yalakweyo mwana chilosyo (chakulosya ukombosi wa Allah) kwa ŵandu ŵaakuchetelela."
  17,34,"Soni ngasinchiŵandichila chipanje cha mwanache jwaŵina ikaŵeje mwitala lyalili lyambone (mpela kuchitupiya ni malonda), mpaka akuyiche komangala kwakwe (ni kumpaga), soni kwanilisyani chilanga, chisimu chilanga chichiŵa chakuwusyidwa (pa Kiyama)."
  17,35,"Soni gumbasyani chipiimo chambale ndema jankupima, soni n’dinjeje nisikelo jakulungamika, yalakweyo ni yaili yambone (kukwenu) soni ni yaikwete mbesi jambone nnope (ku Akhera)."
  17,36,"Soni ngasinyyikuyakuya (pakuiŵecheta kapena kuitenda) ichindu yanganinkola nayo umanyilisi.   Chisimu mawiwi, meso ni ntima ya chilichose cha yalakweyo yichiŵa yakuwusyidwa (ni Allah).",footnotes:1:[Mpela kuŵecheta kwa mundu kwanti: “Naiweni.” Kutendaga pali pangali yaiweni, kapena kuŵecheta kuti: “Mbikene.” Kutendaga pali pangali yapikene.]
  18,1,"Lumbili losope lwene alapikwe Allah Ajula jwantuluchisye kapolo Jwakwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) Chitabu (cha Qur’an), ni nganaŵika nkati mwakwe kupombotala kulikose."
  18,2,"(Achitesile kuŵa) chagoloka kuti chitetele (makafili) ya ipotesi yakandapala yakuuma Kukwakwe, ni chasengwasye ŵakulupilila aŵala ŵaakutenda yambone (pakwapa abali janti), akwete kupata ŵanganyao malipilo gambone."
  18,3,"Tachitama mwalakwe (m’malipilo gambonemo) yakayaka."